Happy birthday my love, I love you more than anything 🤍

#35mm #film #filmphotography #filmcamera #35mmfilm #35mmphotography #analog #analogphotography #analogfilm #blackandwhite #blackandwhitephotography#35mmfilmphotography #stillshootfilm #analogfeatures #ilford #hp5 #onfilm

Words can’t describe our happiness. So excited to share with you that Julie and I are expecting a little baby! I have been taking so much joy photographing Julie’s cute pansita over the last few months. We are taking so many photos and creating so many memories, enjoying every single moment. 
Julie, I can’t wait for you to become the mother of our first child. I can’t wait to witness how amazing of a mother you’ll be to this baby boy. I can’t wait to witness you sharing with him your kindness, your empathy, your passion and all the other things that make you the most incredible human being I have ever met. I’m not the most expressive person but writing has always been my way of sharing my feelings and emotions. For everything that you are and will be, thank you. 
I love you @sincerelyjules
